      <title>美元短缺导致尼日利亚奈拉在平行市场上下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/nigeria-s-naira-falls-on-parallel-market-after-dollar-shortage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于当地货币兑换处停止外币供应，引发人们对美元的争夺，平行市场上尼日利亚奈拉兑美元汇率下跌，与官方汇率的差距扩大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/nigeria-s-naira-falls-on-parallel-market-after-dollar-shortage</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 09:41:58 GMT</pubDate>
